Client -> GW : PATCH /partner-bookings/{booking_id}
activate GW #7c3aed
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #7c3aed

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Current row
deactivate DB
note right of Svc : Merge changed fields only

Svc -> DB : UPDATE ... SET ...
activate DB #FCE4EC
DB --> Svc : Updated row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 200 OK
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 200 OK
